headline: Apartments.com Releases Multifamily Rent Growth Report for July 2025
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., August 08, 2025--Today Apartments.com, an industry-leading online marketplace of CoStar Group (NASDAQ: CSGP), published an in-depth report on multifamily rent trends for July 2025.

headline: Homes.com Report: Moderate Home Price Appreciation Continued in July. Nationally, the Median Home Price Was up 2.1% From a Year Ago.
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., August 08, 2025--Homes.com, a CoStar Group leading online residential marketplace, released a new report today analyzing home price trends in July (based on the data collected to date), including price trends across major metros and house types.
